n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Graham_McTavish\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Graham McTavish\">Graham McTavish</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">TV series</span></th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/House_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"House of the Dragon\">House of the Dragon</a></i>: <a href=\"/index.php/House_of_the_Dragon_-_Season_1\" title=\"House of the Dragon - Season 1\">Season 1</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Harrold Westerling</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Westerling\" title=\"House Westerling\">House Westerling</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Commander_of_the_Kingsguard\" title=\"Lord Commander of the Kingsguard\">Lord Commander of the Kingsguard</a> under King <a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys I Targaryen\">Viserys I Targaryen</a>.\n</p><p>In the television adaptation <i><a href=\"/index.php/House_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"House of the Dragon\">House of the Dragon</a></i>, Harrold is portrayed by <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Graham_McTavish\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Graham McTavish\">Graham McTavish</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-actor_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-actor-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Harrold_Westerling.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/40/Harrold_Westerling.jpg/350px-Harrold_Westerling.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"382\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/40/Harrold_Westerling.jpg/525px-Harrold_Westerling.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/40/Harrold_Westerling.jpg/700px-Harrold_Westerling.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Harrold_Westerling.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Harrold Westerling (Graham McTavish) in <i><a href=\"/index.php/House_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"House of the Dragon\">House of the Dragon</a></i> © HBO</div></div></div>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#House_of_the_Dragon\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>House of the Dragon</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Harrold_Westerling&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>It is unknown when Harrold became Lord Commander of the Kingsguard. At the earliest he could have been the successor of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Ryam_Redwyne\" title=\"Ryam Redwyne\">Ryam Redwyne</a> who died in <a href=\"/index.php/105_AC\" title=\"105 AC\">105&#160;AC</a>.\n</p><p>Upon his own death in <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_112_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">112&#160;AC</a>, Harrold was succeeded as Lord Commander by Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Criston_Cole\" title=\"Criston Cole\">Criston Cole</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_king:_viserys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_king:_viserys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Harrold_Westerling&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Harrold's exact relationship to Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Roland_Westerling\" title=\"Roland Westerling\">Roland Westerling</a> and his daughter, <a href=\"/index.php/Johanna_Lannister\" title=\"Johanna Lannister\">Johanna</a>, is unknown. Roland was head of their House by the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>, and Johanna had married <a href=\"/index.php/Jason_Lannister\" title=\"Jason Lannister\">Jason Lannister</a> to become Lady of <a href=\"/index.php/Casterly_Rock\" title=\"Casterly Rock\">Casterly Rock</a>.\n</p>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Roland_Westerling\" title=\"Roland Westerling\">Roland</a></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\">Unknown<br />wife</td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&